"2 pounds beets (about 6)","2 1/2 cups water","1 tablespoon cider vinegar","1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice","2 teaspoons sugar","1 1/2 teaspoons Dijon mustard","3/4 teaspoon kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","2 tablespoons chopped fresh dill","2 tablespoons finely chopped walnuts"